fields.name: L'Oréal Paris True Match Liquid Foundation
fields.description: Discover True Match, a skincare infused foundation, now available in 48 shades. The formula provides perfect, natural and true-to-skin coverage. Now upgraded with a new skin-matching technology, which includes up to 6 different pigments for a more precise match. Enriched with Hyaluronic Acid. The formula provides up to 24H hydration. Improves skin quality in 2 weeks.

fields.name: e.l.f. Halo Glow Liquid Filter
fields.description: A multi-purpose, liquid glow booster infused with skin-loving ingredients to give your complexion a soft-focus social filter effect IRL. Glowy makeup and skincare hybrid for dewy skin. Complexion looks healthy and more radiant. Liquid Filter can be worn 4 ways: alone, over or under makeup, mixed with foundation, or as a highlighter. Enriched with skin-loving ingredients like Squalane and Hyaluronic Acid. Available in 8 flexible shades that work across all skin tones.

fields.name: NARS Sheer Glow Foundation
fields.description: NARS Sheer Glow Foundation is a glowing, natural radiant finish foundation with sheer and buildable coverage that immaculately evens skin tone. Formulated with skincare benefits and the NARS Complexion Brightening Formula, it leaves skin hydrated, more luminous, softer and smoother. Used daily, Sheer Glow Foundation improves the skin's brightness and texture.

fields.name: Estée Lauder Double Wear Stay-in-Place Foundation
fields.description: Wear confidence with Double Wear Makeup and stay flawless for whatever comes your way. With 24-hour wear, this fresh matte, oil-free makeup controls oil all day. It's sweat-, heat- and humidity-resistant, waterproof, lifeproof and 24-hour colour true. It comes in a wide range of shades that flatters all and it won't look grey on deeper skintones. It unifies uneven skintone and covers imperfections with buildable, medium-to-full coverage that feels lightweight and so comfortable, you won't believe it's long wear. Double Wear is the makeup that keeps up—no matter where your day takes you. Apply it once and don’t think twice. No touchups needed.

fields.name: Studio Fix Fluid Spf15 Foundation
fields.description: For a matte finish that lasts for a full 24 hours, reach for the MAC Cosmetics Studio Fix Fluid SPF15 Foundation. This comfortable foundation delivers medium-to-full buildable coverage with broad spectrum SPF 15 protection, for a breathable, long-wearing and streak-free finish. It applies, builds and blends easily and evenly while controlling oil and blurring pores and imperfections for a non-cakey, smooth result.

fields.name: Makeup Revolution Conceal & Define Foundation
fields.description: Offering lightweight yet buildable coverage, Makeup Revolution Conceal and Define Foundation is available in a range of universally flattering tones. The oil-free, creamy formula dries down to a demi-matte finish without settling into fine lines and creates an even, airbrushed complexion.
